data.description: Exquisite! Custom built home which is perfectly situated on approx. 45+/- acres of unrestricted beautiful land.  There are so many fabulous  amenities which include 5 BR. 5.5 BA, large laundry room, granite countertops, custom built closets, finished basement w/game room, security system, 3 car garage, pool, pool house w/ kitchen & bathroom, and a barn as well.  Amazing property! Comes furnished!
